cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.SD

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language generation of recipes based on user preferences. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a new model for personalized recipe generation using attention fusion layer. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is another possible category as the paper deals with generating natural language instructions from incomplete ingredient details. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a broad category that could also apply as the paper proposes a new task of personalized recipe generation. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is unlikely as the paper does not deal with any audio-related tasks.
